set visualbell
set nu
set surround

" Quit visual mode
vnoremap v <Esc>

" Redo
nnoremap U <C-r>

" Yank to the end of line
nnoremap Y y$

" Tab operation
nnoremap tn gt
nnoremap tp gT

" 设置debug为 zd
:nnoremap zd :action DebugClass<CR>
" 设置run 为 zr
:nnoremap zr :action RunClass<CR>

" built in search looks better
nnoremap / :action Find<CR>
" but preserve ideavim search
nnoremap <Space>/ /
